data.description: You will want to call this one home! This well-appointed house has a great livable floorplan with a 1st-floor master bedroom suite. An impressive 2-story entry is where you will greet your guests. A private den/office is located off the entrance. A formal dining area is the perfect spot for special occasion meals. As you flow into the main living space, you find an open living room and kitchen where memories will be made. The master suite and laundry are off the kitchen. Your master retreat features a spacious bedroom with a French door to the backyard. The master bath combines classic white subway tiles with a neutral patterned ceramic tile floor, a soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and a large closet. The second floor provides a great family room space and 3 bedrooms. On the lower level, you will find 3 additional bedrooms. Ample natural light and recessed lighting throughout. A large rear yard is great for play and gardening. A 3-car attached garage protects your vehicles.
